           SHORT="implementation of the XDG Sound Theme and Name Specifications"
cat <<EOF
libcanberra is an implementation of the XDG Sound Theme and Name
Specifications, for generating event sounds on free desktops, such
as GNOME. It comes with several backends (ALSA, PulseAudio, OSS,
GStreamer, null) and is designed to be portable.
EOF
